data.title: Famous Weddings & Divorces in October 2004
data.meta_description: Famous weddings and divorces in October 2004. See which famous celebrities and historical figures married and divorced in Oct 2004.
data.text:
Famous Weddings

Katey Sagal

"Married ... With Children" actress Katey Sagal (50) weds "The Shield" writer Kurt Sutter (42) in Los Feliz, California

Billy Joel

"Piano Man" singer-songwriter Billy Joel (55) weds American television food critic and chef Katie Lee (23) at 15-acre waterfront estate in Centre Island, New York; divorce 2009

Tiger Woods

Professional golfer Tiger Woods (28) weds former Swedish model Elin Nordegren (24) at Sandy Lane Resort in St. James, Barbados

English actors Matthew Macfayden and Keeley Hawes marry

Actor Marlon Brando's son Christian Brando (46) weds Deborah Presley at The Little White Wedding Chapel in Las Vegas

Joseph Stiglitz

Economist Joseph Stiglitz (61) weds professor Anya Schiffrin (41) at the Municipal Building in New York

"Jackass" member Chris Pontius (30) weds Claire Nolan in Malibu

Travis Barker

Blink-182 pop punk band drummer Travis Barker (28) weds actress and First Runner Up Miss USA 1995 Shanna Moakler (29) at the Bacara Resort & Spa in Santa Barbara, California

Famous Divorces

Actress Andie MacDowell (46) divorces businessman Rhett Hartzog (45) after nearly three years of marriage
